{"tid":1364771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有空請幫拖打倒5毛】被5毛炸既良心ig","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:10:41.000Z","uid":278395,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f18f684efbab1cee387b37aee9149c844deacca","tid":1364771,"uid":278395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"肯係ig表態既藝人/鋪頭得翻好少<br />\n大家真係要幫忙支持佢地<br />\n唔好俾班on 9 5毛瘋狂炸<br />\n除左天佑、HOCC、雞扒妹等藝人<br />\n我見到有個疑似大陸插畫師<br />\n佢有畫香港反送中既插畫<br />\n結果好多5毛衝黎ig 鬧佢<br />\n但無人幫佢還擊 睇到我好激氣<br />\n如果巴打絲打有少少時間<br />\n幫忙入去diu走5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6SXMpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6SXMpL.jpg&h=f0a377f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如巴絲打有發現需要手足入去diu走5毛既page<br />\n可以係下面留低<br />\n大家一齊撐翻自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，我係元屯天人，7月27日不見不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deef74f07f0be40397fa7105582524ba77f778f0","tid":1364771,"uid":278395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"de7f6fbc242195adf2ded41b1691d8c9a6eac260","tid":1364771,"uid":278395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"633bf44fe8e26c2ab4929f200e69f37d087e0d04","tid":1364771,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"方便既話放低條link方便下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3d4def2a44efb94c183d7616214ecfee232bff","tid":1364771,"uid":45007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s